name: InktoberFlashBriefing
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Inktober is a concept that throughout October, you should do at least one drawing a day. As inspiration of what to draw, there are daily suggestions. This flash briefing will remind you to draw something and let you know what the daily suggestion is. For more information about inktober, go to https://inktober.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
